title: How do I install, manage, and uninstall applications?
answer:
You can download application installation packages to a computer, connect your phone to the computer, and use HiSuite to install the applications. You can also download applications from an application store and install them directly on your phone. 

 To check downloaded, running, and all applications, go to Settings and touch All >Manage apps. 

 ![](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=113079)

 On the All tab, touch an application then Disable or Force stop. 

 ![](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=113080)
